/* Value of academic criticism */. Is there any other academic field article that includes “criticism” of the field as a concept? Criticism sections are only really standard for Wikipedia when there are numerous secondary sources that can be synthesized into a substantial, notable portion of the article. One or two authors offhand statements are not noteworthy for a criticism of an academic field of practice. Save those statements for each persons respective Wikipedia article.
